Dialogue: 0,0:00:10.58,0:00:13.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我记得小时候\NI remember when I was a little girl,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:13.81,0:00:16.12,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}爸爸带我去马戏团\Nmy dada took me to the circus --
Dialogue: 0,0:00:16.83,0:00:19.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}那是世界上最棒的演出\NThe greatest show on earth.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:20.20,0:00:24.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}有好多小丑  大象  会跳舞的熊\NThere were clowns and elephants and dancing bears...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:24.94,0:00:27.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}还有一个穿粉色紧身衣的漂亮女士\NAnd a beautiful lady in pink tights
Dialogue: 0,0:00:27.89,0:00:30.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}高高地在我们头顶上飞来飞去\Nflew high above our heads.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.22,0:00:33.14,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我坐在下面观看时\NAnd as I sat there watching,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.17,0:00:37.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}总有一种少了点什么的感觉\NI had the feeling that something was missing.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.68,0:00:39.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我不知道是什么\NI don't know what,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.54,0:00:41.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}但表演结束时\Nbut when it was all over,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:42.49,0:00:44.34,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我对自己说\NI said to myself,
Dialogue: 0,0:00:45.94,0:00:49.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}"马戏团就只是仅此而已吗"\N"Is that all there is to the circus?"
Dialogue: 0,0:00:50.34,0:00:53.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}大事不好  麻烦来了\NUh-oh. Here comes trouble.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:54.81,0:00:57.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我知道你对自己说的话\NI know what you must be saying to yourselves
Dialogue: 0,0:00:58.31,0:01:00.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}"如果她真是这么感觉的话\N"If that's the way she feels about it
Dialogue: 0,0:01:01.95,0:01:04.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}为何她还要待在这里"\NWhy doesn't she just end it all?"
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.92,0:01:06.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}不\NOh, no
Dialogue: 0,0:01:06.71,0:01:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}他一言不发\NCat's got his tongue.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:08.88,0:01:14.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我还没准备好迎接那最终的失望\NI'm not ready yet for that final disappointment.
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.27,0:01:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}因为我知道  我站在这里跟你对话\NFor I know just as well as I'm standing here talking to you,
Dialogue: 0,0:01:18.77,0:01:21.22,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}当最后一刻来临\Nwhen that final moment comes
Dialogue: 0,0:01:21.77,0:01:24.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}当我咽下最后一口气\Nand I'm breathing my last breath...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:26.62,0:01:29.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我会对自己说  "仅此而已吗\N...I'll be saying to myself, "Is that all?
Dialogue: 0,0:01:29.84,0:01:32.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}死亡就是仅此而已吗"\NIs that all there is to dying?"
Dialogue: 0,0:02:52.56,0:02:54.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}亲爱的  你不会还在生的我的气吧\NBaby, you're not still mad at me, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:56.49,0:02:57.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}有吗\NAre you?
Dialogue: 0,0:02:58.12,0:02:59.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}没有  没事了\NNo, it's okay.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:00.28,0:03:01.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}真的  没事了\NReally, it's fine.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:01.98,0:03:04.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我忍不住不告诉他们\NI just couldn't not tell them. You know?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:05.90,0:03:06.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我知道\NI know.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:07.04,0:03:08.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我当时太兴奋了\NI mean, I just get so excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:09.93,0:03:11.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}现在也很兴奋\NAm excited.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:12.29,0:03:13.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}又幸福\NHappy.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:16.08,0:03:18.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我也很高兴  小泰  真的\NI'm glad, Teddy. Me too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:18.71,0:03:19.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}是吗\NYeah?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:22.36,0:03:24.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}当然了\NOf course I am.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:25.85,0:03:27.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}都有点小激动了\NGetting excited a little bit.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:29.68,0:03:31.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}这是上帝的旨意  不是吗\NI mean, God's will, right?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:32.61,0:03:33.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}是啊\NYes.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:46.65,0:03:48.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我爱你  托妮\NI love you, Tawney.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:50.20,0:03:51.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我知道\NI know you do.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:53.02,0:03:54.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我也爱你\NI love you, too.
Dialogue: 0,0:03:57.05,0:03:58.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}是吗\NDo you?
Dialogue: 0,0:03:59.46,0:04:01.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我真的爱你  小泰\NI do love you, Teddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:22.16,0:04:23.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}天哪\NJesus.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:25.12,0:04:27.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你怎么知道我住这里\NHow'd you even know where I lived?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:28.14,0:04:29.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}白页上找的\NWhite pages.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:31.66,0:04:32.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}这样啊\NOh, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:33.43,0:04:34.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}那些东西真是\NThose.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:37.69,0:04:40.73,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}万物的生存和毁灭真是神奇啊  对不对\NIt's amazing what survives and what doesn't, isn't it?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:42.51,0:04:43.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}确实\NIt is.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:44.95,0:04:46.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}该死\NWell, shit.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:47.89,0:04:49.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你来干什么  丹尼尔\NWhat can I do for you, Daniel?
Dialogue: 0,0:04:50.13,0:04:54.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我也不知道为什么今天来\NI'm not sure why today exactly,
Dialogue: 0,0:04:54.08,0:04:55.08,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}但是...\Nbut, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:04:57.05,0:04:58.72,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我想来见你\NI wanted to come and see you.
Dialogue: 0,0:04:59.70,0:05:00.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}是吗\NIs that right?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:01.31,0:05:03.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}跟你说声不要生气\NTo say "No hard feelings."
Dialogue: 0,0:05:03.92,0:05:05.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}好啊\NAll right.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:06.44,0:05:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}没问题  哥们\NSure, buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:08.70,0:05:09.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}谢谢\NThanks.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:13.66,0:05:16.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你一路骑自行车过来的吗\NYou huff it all the way over here?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:18.85,0:05:20.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}其实不远\NIt's not that far.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:20.46,0:05:22.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}也不近吧\NNot that close, either.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:24.15,0:05:26.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你还有什么其他地方要去吗\NGot anyplace else you're supposed to be?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:30.17,0:05:31.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}那就快点进屋吧\NThen get your ass on inside.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:53.41,0:05:55.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}他们给你喝葡萄苏打水了吗\NDid they give you grape soda?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:56.27,0:05:57.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}谁\NWho?
Dialogue: 0,0:05:57.27,0:05:58.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}警察\NThe police.
Dialogue: 0,0:05:59.19,0:06:00.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}那晚\NThat night.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:01.63,0:06:02.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}"那晚"\N"That night"?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:04.72,0:06:07.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}丹尼尔  你就这么直奔主题吗\NWell, damn, Daniel, you just jumping right in, huh?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:09.69,0:06:11.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我不知道  哥们\NI'm not even sure, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:12.89,0:06:14.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我已经不去怎么想它了\NI don't think on it too much anymore.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:17.13,0:06:18.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}好吧\NOkay.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:35.48,0:06:36.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你渴吗\NYou thirsty?
Dialogue: 0,0:06:38.93,0:06:42.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}这是我妻子办教堂活动买的\NMy wife got these for a church thing she had over here.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:43.44,0:06:44.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}一直占着冰箱\NThey've been clogging up the fridge.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:45.24,0:06:46.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}反正是周一早上\NI figure, hey, it's Monday morning.
Dialogue: 0,0:06:46.49,0:06:48.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}成人不妨也来瓶柠檬水喝吧\NMight as well have an adult lemonade.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:00.94,0:07:02.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我们用这个玩过特库摩保龄球\NWe played tecmo bowl on this.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:02.97,0:07:04.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}可不是吗\NYou're damn right we did.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.14,0:07:05.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}确实\NYeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:05.98,0:07:08.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我们结婚时我父母送给我们的\NMy parents gave it to us when we got married.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:08.33,0:07:09.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}一直就放在这里\NIt anchors the room.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:11.62,0:07:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}话说\NSo, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:13.05,0:07:14.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}里面什么样子  兄弟\Nwhat was it like in there, man?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:17.12,0:07:19.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我总得问问你  对吧\NI mean, I got to ask. Right?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:20.37,0:07:21.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}很封闭\NConfining.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:22.62,0:07:25.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}应该就是这样吧\NThat would be the word for it, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:25.85,0:07:28.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}一定程度上很封闭  但是...\NConfining in some ways, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:29.92,0:07:31.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你跟乔治还有联系吗\NDo you still talk to George?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:32.74,0:07:34.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}怎么可能\NDamn, that's a sequitur.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:35.10,0:07:36.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}乔治\NGeorge?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:36.24,0:07:37.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}乔治\NGeorge.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:37.47,0:07:39.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我很久没有看到老乔治...\NI haven't seen old George in...
Dialogue: 0,0:07:39.84,0:07:43.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我们几年前一起去火石河那边钓过鱼\NWell, we went fishing together a couple years ago on the Flint.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:45.12,0:07:46.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}没想到你竟然提到他\NFunny you mention him, though.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:47.87,0:07:49.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我好像给他打过电话\NThought I might give him a call.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:50.08,0:07:53.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}好像给他打过还是确实打过\NThought you'd give him a call or you gave him a call?
Dialogue: 0,0:07:54.66,0:07:55.76,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}别这样  大律师\NEasy there, counselor.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:55.77,0:07:58.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}不要这样咄咄逼人\NDon't go poking me in the chest with no question marks.
Dialogue: 0,0:07:58.97,0:08:00.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我给他打过电话\NI gave him a call.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:01.11,0:08:02.27,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}出于礼貌\NTo be nice.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:02.72,0:08:03.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}但他没理会我\NHadn't heard back.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:05.79,0:08:07.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}他现在住在哪里\NWhere's he live now?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:08.61,0:08:10.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}这玩意儿真难喝  你想喝啤酒吗\NOh, these are terrible. You want a beer?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:13.13,0:08:16.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}乔治住在佛罗里达\NUh... Georgey lives in Florida.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:18.30,0:08:19.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}利夫奥克\NLive Oak.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:20.49,0:08:22.57,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}那里热死了\NSatan's butthole, man.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:27.01,0:08:29.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你不会想伤害他吧\NYou ain't thinking about hurting him, are you?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:32.19,0:08:34.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我不想伤害任何人\NI don't want to hurt anybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:34.50,0:08:36.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我可不想被牵涉到那种事上\N'Cause I wouldn't want to be a part of anything like that.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:38.27,0:08:39.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}什么事\NPart of what?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:39.51,0:08:43.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}但你要去拜访他的话  代我问好\NBut if you go visit him, tell him I said "Hello."
Dialogue: 0,0:08:47.86,0:08:48.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我会的\NI will.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:49.77,0:08:52.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}去拜访他还是代我问好\NGo visit him or tell him I said "Hello"?
Dialogue: 0,0:08:55.75,0:08:57.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}两者都会吧\NBoth, I suppose.
Dialogue: 0,0:08:57.92,0:08:59.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我不确定\NI'm not sure.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:00.78,0:09:02.05,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我该走了\NI should go.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:05.07,0:09:06.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}等等  我说...\NHey. Hey, that's, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:07.45,0:09:09.90,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}利夫奥克离这里很远  哥们\NThat's a long ride down to Live Oak, buddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:10.01,0:09:11.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我会想办法\NI'll figure it out.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:12.06,0:09:13.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}跟你说吧\NI'll tell you what.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:18.83,0:09:20.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}其实今早我该去上班的\NI'm supposed to be at a job this morning,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:20.56,0:09:23.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}可那家伙就是个贱人\NBut he's a cheap son of a bitch, really.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:23.79,0:09:27.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}要不  我们一起去公路旅行吧\NWhat say... We go on a road trip?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:27.74,0:09:28.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我们要先给他打电话吗\NShould we call him first?
Dialogue: 0,0:09:28.95,0:09:31.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}那晚...\NLook, that night --
Dialogue: 0,0:09:32.55,0:09:34.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}或者是那天早上  警察在场...\NOr that morning, I mean, with the police --
Dialogue: 0,0:09:35.06,0:09:38.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我只是说  你跟她在争吵\NAll I did was say you and her were arguing.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:39.52,0:09:40.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}仅此而已\NThat's it.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:40.37,0:09:41.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}是乔治说...\NIt was George who said --
Dialogue: 0,0:09:43.70,0:09:44.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}该死\NHell.
Dialogue: 0,0:09:44.43,0:09:46.51,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你想去跟他谈谈这件事的话\NYou want to go down there, you want to talk with him about it,
Dialogue: 0,0:09:46.51,0:09:49.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}只要你不动粗...\Nas long as you keep it gentlemanly...
Dialogue: 0,0:09:52.51,0:09:54.39,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我乐意开车\N...I am happy to do the driving.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.29,0:10:00.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}好了\NAll right.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:00.87,0:10:03.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}把你的小自行车搬到车上\NPut your little bicycle in the bed there,
Dialogue: 0,0:10:03.13,0:10:04.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你去坐副驾驶\Nand you grab shotgun.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:04.65,0:10:06.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我去方便一下\NI'm gonna piss real quick.
Dialogue: 0,0:10:06.61,0:10:08.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}然后我们就一起上路  哥们\NAnd then we'll hit the road, son!
Dialogue: 0,0:11:11.15,0:11:13.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}收好小桌板  各位乘客\NTray tables up, passengers.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:14.21,0:11:15.82,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}准备起飞了\NPrepare for takeoff.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:39.57,0:11:41.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我有那个的优惠券\NI-I got one for that.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:42.32,0:11:43.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}好啊\NFigured you might.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:47.89,0:11:49.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}一共41.2美元\NYour total is $41.20.
Dialogue: 0,0:11:53.27,0:11:53.96,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}一\NOne...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:55.41,0:11:56.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}二\NTwo...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:57.39,0:11:58.19,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}三\NThree...
Dialogue: 0,0:11:59.93,0:12:00.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}四\NFour...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:02.33,0:12:03.48,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}五\NFive...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:05.34,0:12:06.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}六\NSix...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:08.43,0:12:09.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}七\NSeven...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:11.16,0:12:12.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}八张1块的\NEight $1s.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:14.18,0:12:15.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}这儿有10块呢\NOh, there's that $10.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:15.56,0:12:17.35,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}看到了\NYep. There it is.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:17.71,0:12:19.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}还有20\NAnd...$20.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:19.99,0:12:21.55,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}-现在有...  -38块\N- That's... - $38.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:21.56,0:12:22.50,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}38块\N$38?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:23.08,0:12:24.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}-那我还差...  -差3块2\N- So I'm... - $3.20 short.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:25.79,0:12:26.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}3块2\N$3.20...?
Dialogue: 0,0:12:26.72,0:12:27.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}还差3块2\NShort.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:32.21,0:12:34.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我真不愿意用这些  但是...\NI hate to use these, but...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:37.30,0:12:38.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我不知道这是否...\NI don't even know if that...
Dialogue: 0,0:12:46.40,0:12:48.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}您还差20美分\NYou still owe 20 cents.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:50.31,0:12:52.95,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我记得我这儿有25美分的\NI know I have a quarter in here.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:54.00,0:12:54.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}是枚弗吉尼亚州纪念币\NIt's a Virginia one.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:55.96,0:12:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}-上面刻着"詹姆斯敦"的  -算了\N- Got Jamestown on it. - Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:57.41,0:12:58.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}老天  算了吧\NGod. Forget it.
Dialogue: 0,0:12:59.33,0:13:01.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我替你付这20美分  不用麻烦了\NI will pay the 20 cents. Not a problem, okay?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:11.73,0:13:12.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}真是出人意料啊\NWhat do you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:13.46,0:13:14.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}詹姆斯敦\NJamestown.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:20.95,0:13:23.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}这样就对了\NThat's right... right there.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:25.90,0:13:27.91,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}谢谢你花钱买了这些\NAppreciate you flipping the bill for those.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:28.62,0:13:29.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}味道不错\NTastes good.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:30.72,0:13:32.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}可不  很不错\NYeah, as good as it gets.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:38.63,0:13:41.66,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}老兄  这是真的吗\NOh, man. Unreal.
Dialogue: 0,0:13:41.66,0:13:43.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}-我是说  不可思议  -什么\N- I mean, damn! - What?
Dialogue: 0,0:13:44.00,0:13:45.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你个狗崽子\NYou son of a bitch!
Dialogue: 0,0:13:45.94,0:13:47.63,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}今天早上我从床上爬起来的时候\NWhen I got out of bed this morning
Dialogue: 0,0:13:47.87,0:13:51.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我从衣柜上方的小窗户往外看\Nand I was staring out that little window above our commode
Dialogue: 0,0:13:51.00,0:13:53.33,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}盯着39号公路上的交通灯\Nat the traffic light that's out on 39
Dialogue: 0,0:13:53.34,0:13:56.38,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}就是草地那边那个永远亮着绿灯的交通灯\Nthat is always green out beyond the hayfield,
Dialogue: 0,0:13:56.44,0:13:58.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我绝对想不到  就在今天\NI never would have said, "Well, today's the day
Dialogue: 0,0:13:58.58,0:14:01.60,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我要和丹尼尔·霍顿一起去佛罗里达\Nthat I'm gonna go to Florida with Daniel G.D. Holden."
Dialogue: 0,0:14:01.60,0:14:03.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}绝对想不到\NI mean, never.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:05.00,0:14:06.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}那个交通灯永远是绿灯吗\NThe light's always green?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:07.55,0:14:09.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}反正我从没见过它变红灯\NI ain't never seen it red.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:09.62,0:14:10.69,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}一次也没有\NNot once.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:10.84,0:14:12.10,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}那它为什么在那儿\NWhy's it there?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:15.95,0:14:18.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}有些事儿  你就是无法预料的\NSome things, you just don't see coming.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:19.75,0:14:20.93,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我想你说得对\NI think you're right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:21.06,0:14:22.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我就是对的\NI am right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:27.46,0:14:29.30,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}但我很高兴和你一路前行\NBut I'm glad to be sitting here with you.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:29.95,0:14:30.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}感觉不错\NFeels right.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:33.02,0:14:37.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}感觉像是我们有地方可去\NFeels like we're... going somewhere.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:37.80,0:14:41.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}男女之间的那些妙不可言的一切\NEverything that is good between men and women
Dialogue: 0,0:14:41.01,0:14:44.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}都已融入泥浆和黄油\Nwas written in mud and butter,
Dialogue: 0,0:14:44.87,0:14:46.31,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}还有烤肉酱中\Nand barbecue sauce.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:46.59,0:14:48.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}-你听过吗  -没有\N- You know? - No.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:49.01,0:14:52.84,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}有次我做梦  保拉·迪恩在梦里对我说的\NPaula Deen said that to me in a dream I had one time.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:52.99,0:14:54.36,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}谁是保拉·迪恩\NWho's Paula Deen?
Dialogue: 0,0:14:55.07,0:14:56.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}她是电视节目里的一位厨师\NOh, she's a chef on TV.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:56.79,0:14:57.87,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}她曾经是\NWell, she was.
Dialogue: 0,0:14:59.08,0:15:01.71,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}不知道怎么搞的  现在厨师们都上电视了\NChefs are on TV now, for some reason.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:02.67,0:15:03.85,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}大家都很喜欢看\NPeople eat it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:04.00,0:15:08.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}她就是个乔治亚州奥尔巴尼出来的大火腿\NAnyway, she's just a big ol' ham hock out of Albany, G.A.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:08.45,0:15:11.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}她给北方佬做南方菜\NShe makes southern food for Yankees.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:11.06,0:15:13.01,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我的重点是  在我的梦里\NMy point is, in my dream,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:13.33,0:15:16.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}不知怎的  我和她一起玩激流划艇\NI'm white-water rafting with her, for some reason,
Dialogue: 0,0:15:16.17,0:15:18.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}她对我讲了那番话\Nand, um, she said that to me...
Dialogue: 0,0:15:19.36,0:15:22.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}就在她碰我的小弟弟之前\NRight before she... touched my hamster.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:24.12,0:15:26.37,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}这真是让我难以忘怀  你懂吗\Nbut it stuck with me, you know?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:27.66,0:15:29.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}只有这个梦给我这种感觉\NIt's the only thing from a dream that ever has.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:30.19,0:15:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你经常做梦吗\NDo you dream often?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:31.90,0:15:33.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}不是  几乎从不做梦\NNo. Almost never.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:33.98,0:15:36.99,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我认为我的睡眠质量比所有见过的人都好\NI think I sleep more soundly than anybody I ever met.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:37.55,0:15:39.07,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我敢肯定如此\NIn fact, I know I do.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:41.69,0:15:44.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}倒是你看起来像是经常做梦的人\NNow, you seem the type that does a lot of dreaming.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:45.24,0:15:46.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}有时候吧\NWell, sometimes.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:47.32,0:15:49.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你醒了以后会回想那些梦吗\NYou wake up and think about them?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:49.65,0:15:51.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}那对我来说就是浪费时间\NSeems like a waste of time to me.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:51.92,0:15:53.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}思考它们是一种浪费吗\NA waste to think on them?
Dialogue: 0,0:15:53.77,0:15:57.13,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}当你一觉醒来  回到现实的时候  是的\NOnce you're awake and walking around in the real world, yeah.
Dialogue: 0,0:15:57.13,0:15:59.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我是说你有现实的事情要去处理\NI mean, once there are things to actually take care of.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:00.14,0:16:01.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我不知道\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:01.68,0:16:03.09,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}试图从梦境中找到意义所在\NTrying to find meaning in them...
Dialogue: 0,0:16:03.09,0:16:05.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}试图从任何事情里找到意义所在\Ntrying to find meaning in anything.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:05.71,0:16:08.54,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}如果你当真了  那就是浪费时间\NIt's a waste of time, if you really want to get down to it.
Dialogue: 0,0:16:08.54,0:16:10.32,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}那么生活是毫无意义的吗\NSo life's meaningless?
Dialogue: 0,0:16:12.75,0:16:13.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}谁的生活\NWhose life?
