Dialogue: 0,0:26:18.07,0:26:19.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}认罪协议\NA plea deal?
Dialogue: 0,0:26:20.85,0:26:21.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}他们想要什么\NWhat do they want?
