Dialogue: 0,0:26:24.66,0:26:26.64,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}-然后呢  -然后\N- And? - And...
Dialogue: 0,0:26:28.10,0:26:29.43,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}有期徒刑10年以上\N10 more years.
