Dialogue: 0,0:27:15.82,0:27:17.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}参议员  卡尔\NSenator. Carl.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:18.19,0:27:19.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你们怎么来了\NThis is a surprise.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:20.31,0:27:21.40,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你好吗  小泰\NHow you doing, Ted?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:22.28,0:27:23.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我不确定\NI don't know yet.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:23.67,0:27:27.03,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}小泰  我这也是迫不得已\NTeddy, I want you to know that I absolutely felt like I had to.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:28.91,0:27:29.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}天哪  卡尔\NChrist, Carl.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:30.89,0:27:31.78,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}为什么\NWhy?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:31.90,0:27:33.56,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}只有我们  小泰\NIt's just us now, Teddy.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:34.01,0:27:35.21,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}只有我们干什么\N"Just us" what?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:35.83,0:27:37.15,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}搞什么  卡尔\NGod damn it, Carl.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:37.15,0:27:39.45,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}他并不想背叛你的信任  孩子\NHe didn't want to betray your confidence, son,
Dialogue: 0,0:27:39.74,0:27:41.29,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}但必须如此\Nbut it was the right thing to do.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:41.32,0:27:43.26,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}这很不容易  但却是正确的事\NIt wasn't easy, but it was right.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:43.89,0:27:44.86,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}对谁来说\NRight for who?
Dialogue: 0,0:27:46.21,0:27:47.68,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我们希望你能站出来\NWe want you to come forward.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:47.97,0:27:49.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我们希望你起诉\NWe need you to press charges.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:51.42,0:27:52.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我绝不会起诉的\NThere's no way I'd do that.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:53.43,0:27:54.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}绝对不会\NNo way in hell.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:55.31,0:27:56.97,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你得想想  丹尼尔下一个\NYou need to think about the next person
Dialogue: 0,0:27:56.97,0:27:58.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}会伤害谁\Nthat Daniel has a problem with.
Dialogue: 0,0:27:59.26,0:28:01.24,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你觉得他不会再干了吗\NYou think this was a two-time thing?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:01.63,0:28:02.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}在他那样对汉娜后\NWhat he did to Hanna?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:03.35,0:28:04.61,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}在他那样对你后\NWhat he did to you?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:05.21,0:28:06.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你觉得他会这么容易就收手吗\NThat he's gonna stop,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:06.67,0:28:07.67,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}难道他会痊愈吗\Nlike he's cured or something?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:07.72,0:28:09.28,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}他有强迫症  小泰\NHe has these compulsions, Ted.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:09.28,0:28:11.16,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}他没法控制自己\NIt's as if he can't help himself.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:11.78,0:28:15.11,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}听着  我们那天吵架了\NLook, we got in an argument that night,
Dialogue: 0,0:28:15.45,0:28:16.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}事情有点失控\Nthat has got out of hand.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:17.45,0:28:18.42,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}仅此而已\NThat's all.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:23.45,0:28:24.98,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你继母呢\NWhat about your stepmama?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:26.62,0:28:28.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你父亲  你弟弟呢\NYour daddy, your -- your little brother?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:28.41,0:28:31.06,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}他们都和他生活在一起不是吗\NThey're all living under the same roof with him, aren't they?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:31.06,0:28:32.49,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}他绝不会伤害妈妈的\NHe'd never hurt mom.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:34.01,0:28:35.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}那你妻子呢\NAnd what about your wife?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:38.56,0:28:40.83,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你们吵架就是因为她吧\NThis little argument was about her, initially.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:42.22,0:28:44.94,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你不想让她身处危险吧\NYou don't want to put her in any future danger, do you?
Dialogue: 0,0:28:45.03,0:28:47.46,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我绝不会让那个混蛋再和她单独在一起\NThat son of a bitch is never gonna be alone with her again.
Dialogue: 0,0:28:48.42,0:28:49.81,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}这点我可以保证\NI can promise you that.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:04.93,0:29:07.02,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}这会让我的家分崩离析的\NThis would rip my family apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:10.07,0:29:11.44,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}会让他们崩溃\NRip them apart.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:15.71,0:29:16.79,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我妈\NMy mom...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:18.51,0:29:19.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我爸\NMy dad...
Dialogue: 0,0:29:20.86,0:29:21.89,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}所有人\NEverybody.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:25.47,0:29:26.58,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}就全完了\NIt'd be over.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:30.40,0:29:32.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我理解你  孩子\NI feel for you, son.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:33.30,0:29:34.20,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}真的\NI do.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:35.49,0:29:37.17,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}但是这事不仅关乎你\NBut this is bigger than you --
Dialogue: 0,0:29:37.92,0:29:39.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}甚至不仅关乎你的家人\Nbigger than your family, even.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:42.02,0:29:44.88,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}换句话说  这不是你能控制的\NIn a way, it's -- it's out of your hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:29:45.43,0:29:47.41,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我们都无法控制\NO-out of all of our hands.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:04.84,0:30:05.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}是我编的\NI made it up.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:09.37,0:30:10.65,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我是说\NI mean, uh...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:11.59,0:30:13.18,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我们那天确实吵架了\Nwe got into an argument that night.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:13.18,0:30:15.77,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}这部分是真的\NThat -- that part's true.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:17.48,0:30:19.23,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}但剩下的...\NBut the rest of it, I just...
Dialogue: 0,0:30:21.29,0:30:22.25,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}都是我编的\Nmade up.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:22.88,0:30:25.53,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}你为什么要编这种事\NWhy would you make something like that up, son?
Dialogue: 0,0:30:26.71,0:30:27.80,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我不知道\NI don't know.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:28.17,0:30:29.70,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}也许是因为我喝醉了吧\N'Cause I was drunk, I guess.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:31.07,0:30:32.47,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我错了\NI made a mistake.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:33.67,0:30:37.00,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}抱歉  但我要关店了\NNow, if you'll all excuse me, I got to close the shop up.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:40.17,0:30:41.92,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}这事不会就这么过去的  小泰\NThis ain't going away, Ted.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:42.52,0:30:44.04,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}真相永远不会消失\NThe truth never does.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:44.27,0:30:45.75,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}我说的就是真相\NThat is the truth.
Dialogue: 0,0:30:46.14,0:30:47.59,Default,,0000,0000,0000,,{\fnMicrosoft YaHei\fs14\4a&H80&}请离开吧\NNow, if you'll all excuse me...
